only a little bit i know.It works only 4 converting 23.976 to 25/30 fps
In mkvmerge GUI
add>file u want
select audio>go to format specification
in stretch>type "23.976/25">then start muxing
U'll get the desired file

Note:it only works 4 converting 23.976 to 24/25/30 from lower to high fps but doin vice versa audio cliches occurs for that other softwares are used
In stretch u can type 
for converting 23.976 to 24="23.976/24"
for converting 23.976 to 25="23.976/25"
for converting 23.976 to 30="23.976/30"

U can try on any video of 2-3 min for testing a sample.if u like it then u can surely use in your movies

Thats the little bit i want to share-hope it helps!!!
